<div class="nbunit" id="24Nov1932"><font color="red">24 November 1932</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from J. Ralph Pinker to Paul L&eacute;on): Will you please send me as soon as possible copy of the manuscript of what will form the instalment in &ldquo;Transition&rdquo;. </div>
